# =============================================================================
# Global ignores for the ms-omni-gateway-policies monorepo
# (PDK / Flex Gateway custom policies — Rust + WASM)
#
# Per-policy .gitignore files may add extra rules on top of these.
# =============================================================================

# --- OS / editor cruft -------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- IDE / tooling -----------------------------------------------------------
.idea/
.vscode/
*.iml
.fleet/
.zed/

# --- Rust / Cargo build artifacts -------------------------------------------
# `target/` exists at every Rust project root; commit Cargo.lock for the
# binary/WASM crates (do NOT add Cargo.lock here).
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk

# --- Anypoint PDK build / runtime artifacts ---------------------------------
.pdk/
**/.pdk/
# Compiled custom policy binaries dropped into playgrounds at build time
**/playground/config/custom-policies/*
!**/playground/config/custom-policies/note.txt
!**/playground/config/custom-policies/.gitkeep

# --- Anypoint Flex Gateway secrets (NEVER commit) ---------------------------
# Local Flex Gateway registration produces these — they contain real TLS
# certs, private keys, agent ids, and tenant ids tied to your org.
**/registration.yaml
**/certificate.yaml
**/conf.d/registration.yaml
**/conf.d/certificate.yaml

# --- Generic secret / env files ---------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.sample
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.jks
secrets.yaml
secrets.yml
credentials.json

# --- Logs / temp -------------------------------------------------------------
*.log
log